after each sentence

*Svu* noć sam se prepirao sa njim. (I argued with him all night.)
*Sve* sam ti to već rekao. (I already told you all of that.)
*Svuda* me prate. (They follow me everywhere.)
*Svugde* me traže. (They look for me everywhere.)
*Svuda* se čuje njihov smijeh. (Their laughter is heard everywhere.)